{"published time": "2024-03-27T13:46:00+08:00", "images": ["https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/vijskovi-medyky.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1-12.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2-10.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/3-13.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/4-9.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/5-7.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/6-9.jpg"], "content": "<div class=\"single-content\"><figure class=\"post-thumbnail\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" height=\"675\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-27T13-46-00-08-00/000000.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-27T13-46-00-08-00/000000.jpg\" width=\"1200\"/></figure><!-- .post-thumbnail --><p><strong>The declaration for medical practice for military units is now available through the portal.</strong></p><p>She reported<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/natalia.kalmykova.9/posts/pfbid02JAT8fy1tnn9FaSSoyGPaP2zpqxda2yFgRGxbjzbQrLCh5dLUosRTpSqvqZJjkQvsl\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">deputy</a>Defense Minister Natalia Kalmykov on her Facebook page.</p><p>\u201cIn cooperation with the Ministry of Health of Ukraine and the Ministry of Digital Transformation of Ukraine, we have simplified the process of obtaining permission for medical practice: conveniently, quickly, without unnecessary documents and queues. Now this procedure takes only a few minutes, \u201dNatalia Kalmykova said.</p><div class=\"fotorama--wp\" data-auto=\"false\" data-captiontag=\"dd\" data-columns=\"0\" data-icontag=\"dt\" data-ids=\"556277,556278,556279,556280,556281,556282\" data-itemtag=\"dl\" data-link=\"file\" data-max-width=\"100%\" data-ratio=\"1.1388888888889\" data-size=\"large\" data-width=\"1025\"><div class=\"gallery galleryid-556275 gallery-columns-0 gallery-size-thumbnail\" id=\"gallery-1\"><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-27T13-46-00-08-00/000001.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-27T13-46-00-08-00/000001.jpg\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-27T13-46-00-08-00/000002.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-27T13-46-00-08-00/000002.jpg\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-27T13-46-00-08-00/000003.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-27T13-46-00-08-00/000003.jpg\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-27T13-46-00-08-00/000004.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-27T13-46-00-08-00/000004.jpg\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-27T13-46-00-08-00/000005.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-27T13-46-00-08-00/000005.jpg\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-27T13-46-00-08-00/000006.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-27T13-46-00-08-00/000006.jpg\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl></div></div><p>The filing of electronic declarations through the portal simplifies the process, making it prompt and effective.</p><p>It is a step towards digitalization in the army and avoiding corruption risks.</p><p>The firs